### Test results
- Pitfalls tests: **11 passed, 11 skipped** (skipped = ML-dep tests, require `pip install .[pitfalls]`)
- Full unit suite: **1949 passed, 12 skipped** — 23 pre-existing failures in unrelated modules (auth, health, registry, settings), no regressions introduced

