## Pitfalls UI/UX Fixes & Enhancements

### Context
Post-integration fixes: scrolling, tab layout alignment, tooltips, server restart race condition,
and license/dependency documentation.

### Changes

1. **`src/front/static/global/css/sidebar-layout.css`** — Pitfalls section now uses `display: flex` default (consistent with other sections); removed the `display: block; height: auto` override that was fighting the flex chain
2. **`src/front/templates/partials/ontology/_pitfalls.html`** — Restructured to match the Axioms section pattern: `section-header mb-4` → `card h-100` → `card-body p-0` → `ob-tabs` → `tab-content p-3`; split into **Patterns** tab (checkboxes + All/Fast toolbar + progress bar) and **Results** tab (summary banner + accordion); results pane gets `overflow-y: auto; max-height: calc(100vh - 280px)` via scoped `<style>` for reliable scrolling; Run Analysis button moved to section header top-right
3. **`src/front/static/ontology/js/ontology-pitfalls.js`** — Results tab auto-activates on analysis completion; results badge shows issue count (yellow/green); `_showResults(totalIssues)` signature; `_showError` also switches to Results tab
4. **`src/back/core/external/pitfalls/runner.py`** — `PITFALL_TAXONOMY` enriched with `description` field for all 19 pitfalls (plain-English explanation of what each check detects and why it matters)
5. **`src/front/static/ontology/js/ontology-pitfalls.js`** — Pattern selector renders ⚡ (fast/graph-only) and 💻 (ML-required) speed icons per check; Bootstrap tooltip on ℹ icon shows the description from taxonomy
6. **`scripts/start.sh`** — `uv sync` now always includes `--extra pitfalls` alongside `--extra lakebase` to prevent ML deps being stripped on restart
7. **`requirements.txt`** — Updated from `-e ".[lakebase]"` to `-e ".[lakebase,pitfalls]"` for Databricks Apps deployment
8. **`licenses/README.md`** — Added "Python Libraries (Optional — Pitfalls Detection)" section; added sentence-transformers, scikit-learn, NLTK, SciPy, and D2KLab vendored code to license summary table
9. **`licenses/python/sentence-transformers-LICENSE.txt`** — new (Apache-2.0)
10. **`licenses/python/scikit-learn-LICENSE.txt`** — new (BSD-3-Clause)
11. **`licenses/python/nltk-LICENSE.txt`** — new (Apache-2.0)
12. **`licenses/python/scipy-LICENSE.txt`** — new (BSD-3-Clause)
13. **`licenses/python/d2klab-ontology-pitfalls-detector-LICENSE.txt`** — new (Apache-2.0, vendored code)

